{"_id":"00tibh4cc4hbit00","name":"Friend of the Rabbits","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"179","contentKey":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.friend-of-the-rabbits","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":12,"folderName":"Wonderbedlam","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Amistad con los conejos","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haber capturado al menos un conejo blanco.</p><p>Puedes acercarte a los conejitos blancos sin asustarlos. Obtienes 2 Éxitos adicionales cuando te enfrentas a la amenaza Conejo blanco. Una vez atrapados, tus nuevos amiguitos estarán dispuestos a entregar un mensaje para ti en cualquier habitación de Maravillas. Este don te permite enviar un conejo blanco, incluso a través de puertas aparentemente cerradas.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Wonderbedlam","requirements":"haber capturado al menos un conejo blanco.","scenario":"Wonderbedlam"},"scenario":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"183"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> To have captured at least one White Rabbit.</p><p>You are able to approach the little white rabbits without frightening them. Receive 2 Additional Successes when you face the Threat The White Rabbit. Once picked up, your new little friends will be able to deliver a message for you to any room in Wonder. This Gift allows you to send a White Rabbit even through seemingly closed doors.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Wonderbedlam","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Wonderbedlam","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.friend-of-the-rabbits","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","sourceDirectory":"wonderbedlam","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"To have captured at least one White Rabbit.","limitations":""},"sort":1200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"000ug2vllv2gu000","name":"Lucid Madness","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"179","contentKey":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.lucid-madness","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":13,"folderName":"Wonderbedlam","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Locura lúcida","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haber sufrido los efectos del don Lugar de locura absoluta al menos una vez.</p><p>Lentamente, vas descubriendo cómo hacer realidad tus ideas más extrañas. Puedes gastar 1 Soma para intentar activar la alocada magia de Maravillas. Expresa alguna locura que podrías llevar a cabo, como: “quiero caminar por las paredes” o “quiero que mi brazo se estire de forma desproporcionada”. El Narrador te pedirá una prueba de posición contra un NO proporcional a la locura de tu petición. Si tienes éxito, obtienes el descriptor que declaraste para el resto de la escena; si fallas, has gastado Soma en vano. El efecto de este don también termina cuando alguien manifiesta que lo que estás haciendo es una completa locura.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Wonderbedlam","requirements":"haber sufrido los efectos del don Lugar de locura absoluta al menos una vez.","scenario":"Wonderbedlam"},"scenario":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"183"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Having suffered the Gift Place of Pure Madness at least once.</p><p>You are slowly figuring out how to make the weirdest ideas real. You can spend 1 Soma to try to activate the mad magic of Wonder. State something crazy that you are capable of, such as I want to walk on walls or I want my arm to stretch out of proportion. The Storyteller will ask you for a Position Check against an OL proportional to the madness of your request. If you succeed, you get the Descriptor you declared for the rest of the Scene; if you fail, you have spent your Soma in vain. The effect of this Gift also ends when someone makes clear that what you are doing is utter madness.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Wonderbedlam","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Wonderbedlam","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.lucid-madness","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","sourceDirectory":"wonderbedlam","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Having suffered the Gift Place of Pure Madness at least once.","limitations":""},"sort":1300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"011ensvnnvsne110","name":"The Forgotten Queen (Special Gift for Regina the Thief of Hearts)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"179","contentKey":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.the-forgotten-queen","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":14,"folderName":"Wonderbedlam","specialFor":"Regina the Thief of Hearts","translations":{"es":{"name":"La reina olvidada (don especial para Regina, la Ladrona de Corazones)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> visitar una sala de curas.</p><p>Recuerdos confusos y emociones dolorosas se apoderan de tu mente. Ya has estado aquí como paciente, pero posiblemente hayas olvidado el motivo. ¿Seguro que quieres recordar? Una vez por escena, puedes intentar recordar algo de tu experiencia en Maravillas. Escoge un lugar o un tema del sanatorio y el Narrador te dará información útil sobre su descriptor, don u objetivo. Recordar es doloroso. Durante el resto de la escena, cuando uses uno de tus dones, tira un dado: con un 5 o más pierdes 1 Soma y ya no estás tan segura de ser la reina.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Wonderbedlam","requirements":"visitar una sala de curas.","scenario":"Wonderbedlam"},"scenario":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"183"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Visit a Cure Room.</p><p>Confusing flashbacks and painful emotions grip your mind. You’ve been here as a patient before, but maybe you’ve forgotten why. Are you sure you want to remember? Once per Scene, you can try to remember something of your experience in Wonder. Choose a place or a subject from the bedlam, and the Storyteller will give you useful information about a Descriptor, a Gift, or their Agenda. Remembering is painful. For the rest of the Scene, when you use one of your Gifts, roll a die: on a 5 or higher you lose 1 Soma and you are no longer so sure that you are the Queen.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Wonderbedlam","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Wonderbedlam","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.the-forgotten-queen","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","sourceDirectory":"wonderbedlam","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Visit a Cure Room.","limitations":""},"sort":1400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
